                        <interp inst="t18440819-name-767" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS SINGLETON</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> He had the watches of me between ten and eleven o'clock in the morning.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18440819-name-768" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18440819-name-768" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
